articles.author: Robert Z. Pearlman
articles.title: Russian cosmonauts make quick work of space station spacewalk - Space.com
articles.description: Oleg Kononenko and Nikolai Chub are back inside the International Space Station after just 4.5 hours outside.
articles.content:
Two Russian cosmonauts completed a spacewalk at the International Space Station, wrapping up all of their tasks with time to spare, including the deployment of a radar that they began last year.
